WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
A wide landscape shot shows rows of bare grapevines on a green hillside. In the distance, steep mountains rise under a clear blue sky. The view slowly pans to the right, revealing more vineyards and rolling terrain.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:12.320
The sea comes into view beyond the hills.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:25.600
A man stands by the vines.

00:01:20.800 --> 00:01:22.120
Anastasis points towards the sea behind him.

00:01:41.300 --> 00:01:43.000
Anastasis point to the left, and the camera follows, showing the mountains.

00:01:56.080 --> 00:01:59.120
He points towards the sea behind him.

00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:48.032
The scene cuts to the winery exterior,
showing a sign that reads “Rira Vineyards.”

00:02:53.032 --> 00:02:55.920
A dog is lying on the ground.